# Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

## Project Overview
This project is part of the CodeAlpha Data Analytics Internship. The objective is to perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a dataset to understand its structure, identify patterns, detect missing values, and generate useful insights.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Google Colab
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Files Included
- EDA.ipynb
- Report.pdf
- dataset.csv
- README.md

## Analysis Performed
- Data Loading
- Data Cleaning
- Handling Missing Values
- Descriptive Statistics
- Data Visualization
- Insights and Conclusions

## Conclusion
The dataset was explored successfully using EDA techniques. Visualizations and statistical analysis helped identify important trends and patterns in the data.
